      "November 2, 2012. Wade to Epstein: \"Angola is a big target for our project. Meeting with my friend the daughter of the PR 3rd week of november. If ur arround Paris or London, I can introduce u to her\" (EFTA01978629). Three days later Epstein asked: \"will dos cantos, be in paris on the 29th\" (EFTA01765092-0). He also wrote Wade that \"eike batista from brazil, richest guy thre , would like also to meet with isabel dos santos in london or paris\" (EFTA01976871). Nothing in the archive confirms any meeting took place.",
